Fidus Writer Debian Packaging
==============================

This directory contains Debian packaging files for Fidus Writer.

For complete documentation on building and installing the Debian packages,
please see:

    docs/debian-packaging.md

Quick Start
-----------

Build packages:
    ./build-deb.sh

Install:
    sudo dpkg -i debian-build/fiduswriter_*.deb
    sudo apt-get install -f

Files in this directory:
- control       Package metadata and dependencies
- rules         Build instructions
- changelog     Version history
- copyright     License information
- *.service     Systemd service files
- *.postinst    Post-installation scripts
- *.postrm      Post-removal scripts
- nginx-example.conf    Example nginx configuration
- README.Debian         User documentation (installed with package)

Last Updated: 2025-12-19